title: Bulldogs bounce back, bite Port Orange Atlantic in shutout
text:
Bulldogs bounce back, bite Port Orange Atlantic in shutout 
Sat, Oct 17, 2015 @ 12:14 am 
BOLLES 42 
PORT ORANGE ATLANTIC 0 
The Bulldogs (7-1) used a 28-point second quarter on the way to a 42-0 rout of host Port Orange Atlantic (0-7)... Bolles took advantage of special teams, recovering three loose kickoffs in the first half.
